metadata.name: FOIL
metadata.description:
The SURFACE series is about exploring materials and altering them to appear as another. FOIL was created by manipulating and photographing a piece of translucent film to catch light, and utilizing AI and other digital augmentations to result in a chromatic, foil-like material. 

FOIL is also my genesis AI-generated NFT. 
Dimensions: 3000x3728 px jpg
